1.0.name: wordpress/poppy-videos
1.0.description:
With Poppy´s Videos, you can embed videos from the most popular video sharing portals, as well as files in .flv, .divx, .mp3, .pdf format and office documents (.doc, ppt, É). Also, the videos and files you embed with Poppy´s Videos will be included in your RSS feeds, so your followers won't have to visit your site to enjoy them.

Presently, Poppy´s Videos supports the following video sharing portals:

  • Youtube
  • Blip.tv
  • Vimeo
  • Megavideo
  • Metacafe
  • Revver
  • Veoh
  • Tu.tv
  • Dailymotion
  • CollegeHumor
  • Prusland
  • ZappInternet
  • LiveLeak
  • Qik
  • Dalealplay
  • Google video
  • Stagevu
  • SlideShare
  • screenr

In Spanish:

Poppy´s videos te permite insertar vídeos de las webs de vídeos más populares y archivos .flv, .divx, .mp3, .pdf y documentos de office (.d
